{"tid":288484,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 又黎揀Wireless Gaming Headset 喇喂!","createTime":"2017-06-18T08:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T05:24:55.000Z","uid":32860,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e442987cf65ac79e2b1a9524fa506cc70b7568d","tid":288484,"uid":32860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"其實自己已經內定咗3款, 都睇咗d youtube 片, <br />\n不過都希望有用緊嘅巴打share下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講下條件先:<br />\n1. 舒適  輕 (最怕夾耳, 會頭痛)<br />\n2. 清晰 (玩開R6, Sniper Elite, Ghost Recon, Hitman, Assassin Creed)<br />\n3. 電量勁 (最好有3個鐘以上)<br />\n4. 希望耐用, 最好有5年<br />\n5. 專玩PS4, 其次PC, 遲d會買switch, 相容晒就最好~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. ASTRO  A50 GEN 3 PLAY</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.astrogaming.com/dw/image/v2/AALZ_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-masterCatalog_AstroGaming_RP/default/dw16d07e89/product-images/3AS52-AGW9N-510_primary_2.jpg?sw=720&amp;sh=720&amp;sm=fit\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.astrogaming.com%2Fdw%2Fimage%2Fv2%2FAALZ_PRD%2Fon%2Fdemandware.static%2F-%2FSites-masterCatalog_AstroGaming_RP%2Fdefault%2Fdw16d07e89%2Fproduct-images%2F3AS52-AGW9N-510_primary_2.jpg%3Fsw%3D720%26sh%3D720%26sm%3Dfit&h=eb1a0658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nhigh-end唔洗講, 超靚仔非常合眼緣,<br />\n但見過有人話易壞, 同埋有d重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. STEELSERIES ARCTIS 7</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vsgamers.es/thumbnails/images/products/3468/gallery/16762/en-headset-gaming-71-wireless-steelseries-artic-7-black.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vsgamers.es%2Fthumbnails%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2F3468%2Fgallery%2F16762%2Fen-headset-gaming-71-wireless-steelseries-artic-7-black.jpg&h=9d2b7827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相對平, 3款最輕最吸引我, 但如果有更好選擇唔介意比多少少<br />\n另外見佢個耳仔位比較細, 怕夾耳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. LOGITECH G933</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src